To install Ansible :

sudo apt install ansible
ansible –version

login into main server-- 

ssh-keygen(generatepublic/privare keypair)
ssh ipaddress(targetfile)
cat fileaddress (to view public key)
copy public key 

enter into target server--
ssh-keygen
vim  ~/.ssh/authorized_keys
paste public key
ssh ipaddress(targetfile)
create inventory file(paste private address of target server)
ls ~/.ssh
vim  ~/.ssh/authorized_keys

Ansible adhoc Commands:
ansible -i inventory all -m “shell” -a “filename”

To write playbook:

vim filename.yml

ansible-playbook -i inventory filename.yml(run)
